comments: Porzingis (DAL) makes marginal contact to Hood's (POR) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) makes marginal contact to Kleber's (DAL) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) maintains legal position as body contact occurs with Doncic (DAL) during his driving shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) places his arm to McCollum's (POR) front during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) and Covington (POR) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Covington (POR) moves alongside of Doncic's (DAL) path after his gather and absorbs the contact during his shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) makes marginal contact to McCollum's (POR) body as they pursue the loose ball.
Richardson (DAL) places his arm to Lillard's (POR) front during his drive and contact affects his SQBR.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) commits  a take foul on McCollum (POR).
Covington (POR) and Kleber (DAL) engage and disengage with another off ball.
McCollum (POR) has his arm extended and he grazes Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) arm as he enters his upward shooting motion and the contact is marginal.
McCollum (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in Richardson's (DAL) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Kleber (DAL) commits a take foul on Anthony (POR).
McCollum (POR) places his hand to Richardson's (DAL) side and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Richardson (DAL) grasps Lillard's (POR) arm off ball and disengages prior to gathering the inbound pass.
